{
  "stem": "15393.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But no, nothing-- not a sound, not a motion, not from this one, not from the other one on the other side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, you can't-- you can't possibly assume that suddenly they went blind or deaf or something-- no.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was just one of those things, one of those miraculous escapes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also like I say, I call these people these sort of unsung heroes because this was-- these were two men who obviously knew who I was, there's no doubt about that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could have had me, they could have easily, there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did nothing, they let me go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, they allowed me to escape, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's the way I look at it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know who I-- I wish I could have known who they were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would have thanked them at some point later in my life, maybe I'd have visited them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there they were, ordinary soldiers standing guard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so I was on my way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I walked and walked and walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, of course, the problem started that I don't know what time it was, but it was nearing early hours of the morning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother was quite a long way away from where I-- from where I was at the moment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I decided I will have to take a tram.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I can't walk through town the way I am because I'm, you now, I mean, a catch 21.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Can't walk like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And anyway, the curfew was on and so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I walked up to the terminal, tram terminal, which were not far away from there, I knew about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I put myself into a tram which was going in the direction where my mother was.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
